milestones.description: Brijesh Patel has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 233 runs, going past Viswanath's 223
Glenn Turner has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (16) for NZ, going past Collinge
Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (11) for IND, going past Viswanath
John Wright and Bruce Edgar's 100-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 73 between Glenn Turner and Jock Edwards
Gavaskar and Kapil Dev's 40-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Viswanath and Kapil Dev
